title: After three years of war with Russia, Ukraine could be heading for an even more dangerous peace deal
cleaned_sentences: LONDON – Ukraine marked the third anniversary of the Russian invasion on Feb 24 with a solemn ceremony in Kyiv, the capital, attended by 12 European heads of state and government, with many more joining by video link.
Three years of absolute heroism of Ukrainians,” President Volodymyr Zelensky told his guests before thanking “all those who defend and support” Ukraine.
